      {
        "id": "R1ZWWXI1PYM6FM",
        "asin": "R1ZWWXI1PYM6FM",
        "title": "Pretty happy with this cooling bandana - especially for the price!",
        "link": "https://www.amazon.com/gp/customer-reviews/R1ZWWXI1PYM6FM/ref=cm_cr_dp_d_rvw_ttl?ie=UTF8",
        "text": "I am honestly pretty happy with this product, especially for the price. I’ve used it several times now on 5 to 6 mile hikes or 3 mile runs with my dog what temperature is in the 80s. Even once it dries out, she still feels cool underneath the bandana. It’s easy to just use my Camelback or water bottle to add a little water every so often if we are going to be out for a while. The colors are fun and I like that the product is lightweight. I’ve already run them through the washing machine a couple of times and they seem to be holding up well. I will say that I do fuss with it a little bit to try to keep it close to her - I tend to tuck it underneath her harness and have to adjust it every so often, but I don’t mind that. I would love to buy a vest for my dog in this same material!",
